reviews.text: You walk into this shop and you first smell amazing coffee.  Oh its so good. Then you hear great music, not too loud ,not too soft adding to a great vibe....
Both the atmosphere and the coffee are high octane. This is a full on PNW style hipster coffee bar experience.  I loved all of the plants, the high ceilings...
I went here recently for a coffee with my partner, and she loves coffee. I wanted to check out this place as it had been shouted out by others in my insta...
